---
// Hero, Section 1
// Typo-only, paper background, massive Sentient headline
---

<section class="hero" aria-label="Hero">
  <div class="wrap">
    <p class="eyebrow">Camplo · Agence camping · Québec</p>

    <h1 class="headline">Un logiciel qui date <em>pas</em> de 2008.</h1>

    <p class="subtext">
      Un CRM et un site de réservation modernes, conçus pour les campings
      indépendants du Québec. On remplace votre vieux système, on ne s'ajoute
      pas par-dessus.
    </p>

    <div class="cta-row">
      <a href="#contact" class="btn-primary">Parler à Camplo</a>
      <a
        href="https://delajoiequebec.com"
        class="btn-secondary"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener"
      >
        Voir Camping de la Joie →
      </a>
    </div>

    <p class="meta">
      <span>Français</span>
      <span>·</span>
      <span>Conçu au Québec</span>
      <span>·</span>
      <span>Depuis 2026</span>
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero {
    background: var(--paper);
    padding: clamp(40px, 5vw, 80px) 0 clamp(80px, 10vw, 140px);
  }

  .eyebrow {
    font-family: var(--font-label);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.16em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--fern);
  }

  .headline {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: clamp(56px, 9vw, 128px);
    letter-spacing: -0.025em;
    line-height: 0.98;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin-top: 28px;
    max-width: 16ch;
  }

  .headline em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--marmalade);
  }

  .subtext {
    margin-top: 32px;
    max-width: 58ch;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: clamp(17px, 1.4vw, 20px);
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
  }

  .cta-row {
    margin-top: 40px;
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 20px 28px;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--marmalade);
    color: var(--paper);
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 15px;
    letter-spacing: 0.01em;
    padding: 18px 28px;
    border-radius: 0;
    transition: background 160ms ease;
  }
  .btn-primary:hover {
    background: var(--marmalade-bright);
  }

  .btn-secondary {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 15px;
    color: var(--fern);
    border-bottom: 1px solid currentColor;
    padding-bottom: 3px;
    transition: color 160ms ease;
  }
  .btn-secondary:hover {
    color: var(--fern-deep);
  }

  .meta {
    margin-top: clamp(48px, 6vw, 72px);
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 12px;
    font-family: var(--font-label);
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--ink-muted);
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }
</style>
